reviews.text:
The location is quite good - by the shore, nice view. (Those would of been 5-star) Food on the other hand, no star. Service was just alright. 

Very low quality of food - they put pieces of kraft cheese in the lasagna. Bad. Not only that, beef is also dry and too much salt. And they put salt in everything including the salad on the side. 

And the drinks - I ordered iced tea. Thought it would be fresh. It turned out just from a canned Nestea 

Anyway would be good if you just wanna grab a beer and sit outside. (Doesn’t require any cooking)
Not so many food options for someone who doesn't eat meat nor dairy. But the drinks are very good! Nice hang out spot.
f*ckin racist🤚🤚🤚🤚 they give you a menu with higher price if you are a foreigner🤮🤮🤮🤮 thanks you ruined my day!! *RUDE AS HELL*
Went here during weekday for a dinner, food is decent. Price is okay for its location. Within 200hkd, you get a soup, a main and a drink.
